                      How To Get Involved [spacer.gif]


    Whether you are a teacher, parent, grandparent, community member, or
    student, you can get involved. As the Cesar Chavez Day approaches you
    can develop your own project to benefit your local community. GO SERV
          has developed a toolkit to help you prepare for the day.

   There are so many ways that you can help put the values exemplified in
                  the work of Cesar E. Chavez into action.
     * Create your own service project using our toolkit
     * Review our list of things you can do
     * Become an AmeriCorps volunteer

        Remember to register your project and its accomplishments!
